Messaging and usage

Explore our recommendations on how Partners and users should talk about their use of, and relationship with, Wix Studio.

What is Wix Studio?

Wix Studio is an end-to-end platform for designers, devs and marketers in agencies and enterprises. Smart design capabilities, flexible dev tools and built-in AI give complete design control for exceptional results. Combined with multi-site management, the platform provides everything needed for a super seamless workflow.
 

What is our brand promise?

"Deliver brilliance. Smash deadlines." With Wix Studio, agencies and enterprises can create, develop and manage exceptional web projects with hyper efficiency.

What are our core benefits?

  • Advanced, precise design tools

  • Innovative built-in AI tools

  • Flexible development capabilities

  • Best-in-class SEO and integrations

  • Native business solutions

  • Comprehensive, multi-site management

  • Enterprise-grade infrastructure

What is our tone & voice?

We speak to our audience just like how they talk, how you talk, how we all talk at work. Our voice sounds like a young, smart web professional in conversation with other web pros. The tone at its core is human, confident, precise and current.

Do’s & Don’ts

  • Do distinguish the brand. Wix Studio is a part of Wix.com Ltd., but it is a distinct offering from Wix. Please make this clear in all of your communications.

  • Do describe sites and apps built on Wix Studio as “Made with Wix Studio”.

  • Do always use a capital S and a space between the words when referencing "Wix Studio".

  • Do direct clients to our homepage and This is Studio video for more detailed information.

  • Don’t include the Wix Studio company name in your company name or any iterations of your company name. E.g. in email addresses, domains, social handles, etc.

  • Don’t use the Wix Studio company name, logo or identity in your promotional campaigns or merchandise. Suggesting your communications are from official Wix Studio channels is strictly prohibited.

  • Don’t modify or alter our brand assets, or use them in a way that is disparaging to Wix Studio.

  • Don't feature Wix Studio on any materials that violate our Terms of Use.

Got more questions?

For any questions about the Wix Studio brand and design assets we haven't covered here, please contact studiobrandassets@wix.com.
